Package org.eclipse.mosaic.lib.routing.graphhopper.util

Class WayTypeEncoder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.graphhopper.routing.ev.IntEncodedValueImpl
      • org.eclipse.mosaic.lib.routing.graphhopper.util.WayTypeEncoder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.graphhopper.routing.ev.EncodedValue, com.graphhopper.routing.ev.IntEncodedValue
    public class WayTypeEncoder
extends com.graphhopper.routing.ev.IntEncodedValueImpl
    Stores additional properties on an edge to describe the way-type of an edge. It does so by encoding the way-type, and some boolean flags based on this way-type, within one integer field by using bit-masking.
